name: Ego T CE4
description:
The EGO-CE4 builds on the achievements of the EGO. Its huge battery enables over 800 puffs a day. The CE4 is the powerful e-cigarette to use a clearomizer to hold a large capacity of 1.6ml e-liquid and the volume of existing eliquid can be easily monitored. This revolutionary new CE4 e-cigarette would last you all day long without often refilling e-liquid. 

The EGO-CE4 consists of CE4 clearomizers and batteries. It offers 5 times as many puffs as other normal e-cigarette. The CE4 gives realistic feel and provides lots of vapour with mechanisms inherited from the EGO double air circulation system. The new power saving battery function improves the efficiency of power consumption. 

Starter often use their first e-cigarette that looks like a traditional tobacco cigarette. However, a short life of battery of those smaller models can be frustrating. The EGO-CE4 1100mAh deluxe kit uses massive 1100mAh batteries and can continuously be vapoured for up to 15 hours without charging, also, its clearomizer holds 1.6ml e-liquid that can last for approximately 500 puffs. 


This kit comes with:

2 x EGO 1100mAh Manual Batteries (batteries now come with 5 click lock feature by popular demand!) available in black or silver batteries.
2 x CE4 Clearomizers (Empty CE4 Clearomizers - require to buy E-Liquid separately)
1 x USB Charger 
1 x USB to UK Mains Charger
1 x Ego Carry Case 
1 x 10ml empty e-liquid bottle

Please Note varies colours (all colours are shown in picture) are available so please advise what colour Clearomizers you would like on purchase.

name: CE4 Clearomizer/Atomizer (3 Pack)
description:
Ego CE4 Clearomizer is a component of Ego CE4 or Ego TANK  electronic cigarette. It holds 1.6ml e-liquid that can last for approximately 500 puffs. 

Ego CE4 Clearomizer although made to a very high standard do breakdown with use, it is always advisable to have a few spare ones.

Ego CE4 Clearomizer fits all Ego, Ego-T batteries.

Varies Colours available please advise which colours you would prefer on purchase if message is not left we'll send a plain/clear CE4 Clearomizer/Atomizer.

name: E-Cigarette Kit
description:
The E-Cigarette is one of the most compact electronic cigarette kits currently on the market. The great thing about the E-Cigarette is that the handy charger and case carries everything you need in one compact unit. The case is designed to be pre-charged so that you can keep your batteries charged on the move. The E-Cigarette is a two-part design with an automatic battery and a pre-filled cartomizer. The E-Cigarette case holds one ready assembled and ready to use electronic cigarette, It also contains the capacity to carry up to 6 filled cartomizers. If you want an electronic cigarette that looks like a real cigarette, performs like a real cigarette and delivers great value, then the Microlite is the e-cigarette for you.

What's Included:

Features: you can recharge the case and the 
case can store power and recharge the battery for 10 times
1 x portable rechargeable Lithium case
1 x Reusable Atomization Device
1 x rechargeable lithium Ion Batteries
6 x Disposable cartomizers (pre-filled) either menthol or tobacco (approx. 300 puffs per cartomizer)
1 x usb adapter
1 x uk charger



Warranty 
The batteries and atomizers contained in each kit have a 28-day parts warranty. The chargers have a 12-month warranty, which covers the component parts; this does not cover damaged wiring or improper use. 
If any parts are found to be faulty within this time please contact our customer service team via email, and we will arrange for a replacement. We may require the goods to be returned for further investigation. 
Product Care 
Users should store and handle these items with special care. We advise electronic cigarette users not to store their e-cigarettes with metallic, magnetized or electronic transmitting devices such as keys or mobile phones, therefore extending the lifespan of functional use.

name: Ego Tank
description:
The Tornado Tank is a revolutionary electronic cigarette, which changed the face of vaping overnight.
Traditional electronic cigarettes had a cartridge and atomizer system which, whilst functional, did not replicate accurately enough the sensation of smoking for many users.
The Tornado Tank changed all of that with its unique fluid feeder system and Tank (T)-atomizer.
The tank holds 1.1ml of fluid in a cartridge that also cleverly incorporates the vapour tube in a single reusable cartridge. The cartridge is held in the atomizer tube and the atomizer ‘spike’ connects the cartridge fluid to the atomizer heating element in a simple but extremely effective practical design. The Tank electronic cigarette comprises of just 3 parts: the atomizer and cartridge as described and a rechargeable battery. Screw the battery onto the atomizer, insert an e-liquid containing cartridge and you are ready to vape. And a battery charger, and a user guide are included and you have all you need in a single kit!

What’s included?
2 x Black Re-chargeable 650 mAh lithium batteries
2 x Cone Shaped Tank Atomizer's.
1 x Mains to USB Wall Charging Adapter.
1 x High Speed USB Charging lead.
5 x Tank Cartridges.
1 x User manual.

Please be aware: the tank cap is designed as a one use only item. However most users will find their cartridge can be re-filled more than once. We only guarantee each tank cap for a single use. If the fluid appears to be leaking from the atomizers- it is more likely that the end cap has been damaged from protracted use and just needs replacing. We have included some spare caps with your purchase. 

Warranty
The batteries and atomizers contained in each kit have a 28-day parts warranty. The chargers have a 12-month warranty, which covers the component parts; this does not cover damaged wiring or improper use.
If any parts are found to be faulty within this time please contact our customer service team via email, and we will arrange for a replacement. We may require the goods to be returned for further investigation. 
Product Care
Users should store and handle these items with special care. We advise electronic cigarette users not to store their e-cigarettes with metallic, magnetized or electronic transmitting devices such as keys or mobile phones, therefore extending the lifespan of functional use.
